                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> There was no other boy in the shop—a boy came to the door for a halfpenny worth of bread before that—I am certain the prisoner is the person who came into the shop, and no one else.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
